532,754 UNI (US$5.33 million), a profit of $579,000 (+12%); 
197,451 LINK (US$4.29 million), a loss of $426,500 (-9%); 
3,862 MKR (US$3.77 million), a loss of $1.7 million (-31%); 
5.153 million ENA (US$3.39 million), a loss of $1.39 million (-29%). 
